We heard your feedback and have made major improvements to the app - including a brand new name - Welcome to Display! We’ve updated the registration and onboarding process so you can have a quick and easy time getting started. Once you’re in you’ll see our brand new feed - where your content is front and center. Swipe up to see the next post, video, bit of magic, and don’t forget to tap support on the ones you love. Display may look different, but we’re still about giving creators a level playing field and an opportunity to see their hard work add up.

Oh yeah, we brought in an exterminator for all the pesky bugs - let us know if we missed any.
